title: South Korea Liquidity Adjustment Loans Rate
description: South Korea Liquidity Adjustment Loans Rate was at 4 percent on Thursday November 10. Lending Rate in South Korea averaged 2.06 percent from 2019 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 4 percent in October of 2022 and a record low of 1.50 percent in May of 2020. This page provides - South Korea Liquidity Adjustment Loans Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: The Bank of Korea
